title: OUCH! Dana Loesch ponders if Elizabeth Warren will appropriate Cherokee (again) to run for WH
text:
OUCH! Dana Loesch ponders if Elizabeth Warren will appropriate Cherokee (again) to run for WH Posted at 2:26 pm on February 10, 2017 by Sam J. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
After the past week there is a good chance that Elizabeth Warren may be looking at a possible run for the White House in 2020. So you gotta wonder if and when she does run, will she play the Cherokee card … When Warren tries to run for the WH will she use the "first women of color" line again like she did in '93 when appropriating Cherokee? 
— Dana Loesch (@DLoesch) February 9, 2017 
It’s interesting how the Left allows her to get away with such a gross misrepresentation of who she is. Wait, it’s not interesting, it’s actually sad and totally expected at this point. Carry on. 
— Vern Demerest —✈ (@TxAv8r) February 9, 2017 Trending
